==Specialized engines/engine middle-ware== {{Unsourced-section|date=January 2018}} Some features may be integrated into engines. For instance for trees and foliage a special "engine" is available, [[SpeedTree]], that does just that (or could be integrated into general engines). The [[Euphoria (software)|Euphoria]] character's 3D animating engine can be used independently but is integrated in the [[Rockstar Advanced Game Engine]] and the game ''[[Grand Theft Auto IV]]''.
